- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper mentions applications in telecommunications and energy distribution networks, which are relevant to networking and internet architecture. 
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory): The paper mentions the concept of traversal cost, which is a measure of cost in game theory. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper presents hardness results and polynomial-time solvable special cases, which are topics in data structures and algorithms. 
- cs.AL (Algorithms): The paper focuses on finding a proper edge coloring to minimize costs, which is a problem that can be solved using algorithms.
